## Design System — Stella Portfolio

### Colors
- Background: #F8F8F4
- Text: #1A1A16
- Accent: #4A7C59
- Surface: #E8EBE4

### Typography
- Headlines: Cormorant Garamond, serif
- Body: system-ui, sans-serif
- H1: 4rem
- H2: 2rem
- H3: 1.25rem
- Body: 1rem, line-height 1.7

### Spacing
- Section padding: 120px vertical
- Card gap: 24px
- Max content width: 1100px
- Page margin: 48px horizontal

### Components
- Card border-radius: 12px
- Button border-radius: 24px
- Button style: outlined, 1px solid accent, transparent background

### Accessibility
- WCAG 2.2 Level AA at all times
- prefers-reduced-motion always respected
- Visible focus indicators always on
- Semantic HTML always

### Tone
- Minimalist, lots of whitespace
- No decorative elements unless intentional
- Reference aesthetic: mattfredette.com
